        <mxCell id="nfoEANW8VW_5X_dOmgvR-168" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Note 1:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 102, 102);&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Não é possível garantir, no modelo relacional, a participação total de &quot;Requisição&quot; com &quot;Lote de Item&quot;&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=nowrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="69.94999999999999" y="731" width="800" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nfoEANW8VW_5X_dOmgvR-169" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Note 2:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(245, 245, 245), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Mapeamos a FK de &quot;Req. Entrega&quot; para a tabela &quot;Entrega&quot; para garantir a participação total usando Not Nul&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(245, 245, 245), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;l&lt;/font&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=nowrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="69.94999999999999" y="760" width="800" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nfoEANW8VW_5X_dOmgvR-170" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff0000&quot;&gt;Note 3: &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;As subentidades de &quot;Usuário&quot; e &quot;Requisição&quot; possuem relacionamentos próprios, as especializações são disjuntas e&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(245, 245, 245), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;possuem um atributo identificador. Logo, o procedimento padrão 1 é adequado&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=nowrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="70" y="801" width="799.95" height="23" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="nfoEANW8VW_5X_dOmgvR-171" value="&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(255, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Note 4:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ff0000&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;As subentidades de &quot;Avaliação&quot; possuem relacionamento próprio e a especialização é disjunta, porém sem atributo identificador.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Logo, o procedimento padrão 2 é adequado&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=nowrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="69.95" y="844" width="810.05" height="30" as="geometry" />
